{
  "stem": "5371.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name was Bruno.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was in there for sabotage, because I know he-- I remember he had a-- a black triangle.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But his number was number 1.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was caught, you know, with an SS woman in bed, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's what the story was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's what the story was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was relieved of his job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in came in another German, with a red triangle, a political.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He had a number 62,000-- I don't remember-- the other numbers, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I remember 62,000, because I saw him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my kapo came over to me, and he said to me-- and he knew that I had-- because he was the one who-- to tell me that I had a death sentence.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He told me there is a chance that my sentence could be taken out from the-- if it is in the camp chancellery, there's a possibility to take that sentence out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If it's in the SS chancellery, then is no way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- but he said to me but he needs a ladies-- a gold ladies' watch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't-- I had no means of getting anything like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But while we were working already on construction, we put up buildings for the Germans, storage houses like.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And over there I met people from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew a cousin of mine was working in-- in the Sonderkommando, which was the crematorium, also a couple men from my hometown and a cousin of mine from a neighboring town.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said to a man from my hometown, also, named Braun, I said to him, if he can talk to them, I need-- and I told him the story, that I need a ladies' gold watch, if they can bring it to me.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
